# The `DWARFContext` Class Reference

<DoxygenPage pluginConfig={pluginConfig}>

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarfcontext">DWARFContext</a> This data structure is the top level entity that deals with dwarf debug information parsing. <a href="#details">More...</a>

## Description {#details}

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarfcontext">DWARFContext</a> This data structure is the top level entity that deals with dwarf debug information parsing.

The actual data is supplied through DWARFObj.

Definition at line 48 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/debuginfo/include/llvm/debuginfo/dwarf/dwarfcontext-h">DWARFContext.h</a>.
